{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Follow the war paths</h2>The Winds of Change DLC bring a vast array of new content and systems to Regiments!<br><br><br>Navigate the unpredictable nature of war in the all-new procedurally-generated 'War Paths' mode.  Lead a selected Regiment through dozens of battles, evolve its organization, overcome challenges, lament your losses, fight, survive, and if it all comes crashing down, try again.<br><br><br>Lead one of the many new French, Dutch, Canadian, or Czechoslovakian regiments as they enter the fray, spanning more than 70 new units! Experiment with new tactics as additional air assets such as heliborne infantry redefine the very shape of the battlefield!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Main features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Experience twisting, procedural campaigns in the new War Paths mode<br></li><li>Fight alongside or against new units from French, Dutch, Canadian, and Czechoslovak regiments, all ready to bring their own style of fighting to the battlefield<br></li><li>Strike from the sky with new tactical possibilities heralded by the addition of heliborne troops and fighter jets!<br></li><li>Command more than 70 new vehicles and weapon systems, all meticulously modelled with the kind of detail you've come to expect from us in the base game</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Soar on the Winds of Change</h2>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542770/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727655833","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542770/page.bg.jpg?t=1727655833","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542770/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1727655833","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542770/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1727655833","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Downloadable Content","id":21},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":